content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1262.5 - Vehicles to yield right of way to aircraft

State Regulations

All ground self-propelled vehicles shall yield the
right-of-way to any and all aircraft in motion, except emergency equipment
which shall have tower clearance when responding to an alarm. Notes
